    <summary>This extension adds the facility to manage your videos associated with Magento products in the same way you manage the images from the Magento admin panel. </summary>
    <description>Provide your customers with easy access to How-to Videos, Video Reviews, Product Demonstrations or any videos you think your customers would like to see.&#xD;
&#xD;
This extension adds the facility to manage your videos associated with Magento products in the same way you manage the images from the Magento admin panel. &#xD;
&#xD;
1)	Simple Admin interface similar to the &#x201C;Images&#x201D; tab on the product admin page.&#xD;
2)	Easy to upload videos to a product. &#xD;
3)	Supports .mp3, flv file formats for video uploading.&#xD;
4)	Facility to embed code of YouTube, Vimeo, Brightcove, TidalTc, Wistia, Kaltura, Dailymotion, LongTail, thePlatform and Sublime.&#xD;
5)	Manage all the uploaded videos by simply editing a product&#xD;
6)	Facility to define the maximum limit for uploading the videos &#xD;
7)	Multi-store compatible. Ability to manage videos at the Website, Store, or View level&#xD;
8)	Automatically uploads your company&#x2019;s logo as video thumbnail for you &#xD;
9)	Upload custom images for thumbnails&#xD;
10)	Facility to manage the configuration for Max Video Uploading Limit and Max Video Size. &#xD;
</description>
